Acme::use::strict::with::pride version 0.01
===========================================

Enforce bondage and discipline on very naughty modules.

Some people say that use strict is gay;
Others think that it's cool.
This module lets you use strict with pride.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  perl 5.6.0 or later
  Test::More (of Borg. You will be assimilated)

